Package: CorrSurvBinom
Title: Analysis of correlated time-to-event and binary outcomes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
person(given = "Gosuke",
family = "Homma",
role = c("aut", "cre"),
email = "my.name.is.gosuke@gmail.com")
Description: Provides functions to generate pseudorandom numbers of correlated
time-to-event and binary outcomes using copula-based approaches. This
package is particularly useful for simulation studies in biostatistics,
survival analysis, and clinical trial design where correlated outcomes
need to be modeled.
